videos.description: Rashard Kelly makes the jumper after drawing the contact from the defender, which leads to the 3-point play for Wichita State.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Kelly makes tough and-1 bucket

videos.description: Darral Willis Jr. beats the double-team by finding Rashard Kelly underneath for the dunk.
videos.headline: Extra pass leads to dunk for Shockers

videos.description: Conner Frankamp finds Rashard Kelly for the corner jumper and then hits the pull up 3-pointer in transition to extend Wichita State's lead over Bradley.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Frankamp doing it all

videos.description: Wichita State's Markis McDuffie steals the Bradley inbound pass and goes coast to coast for the wide open dunk.
videos.headline: Bradley mistake leads to fastbreak dunk for Wichita State

videos.description: Antoine Pittman comes up with the steal and throws down the dunk as Bradley tries to cut into the huge Wichita State lead.
videos.headline: Bradley tries to get back in it with dunk
